Install acl_server on Cumulus Linux
-----------------------------------

Copy acl_server to /etc/init.d/

On Cumulus Linux 3.0 also install the systemd service file
Copy acl_server.service to /lib/systemd/system/

Start acl_server daemon.

WARNING
Script provides no access controls. Installing a web server (Apache/NGINX) to
reverse proxy acl_server is a simple way to add access controls, encryption,
authentication etc.

To limit access to localhost, change the line:
server = HTTPServer(('',8080), ACLRequestHandler)
to:
server = HTTPServer(('127.0.0.1',8080), ACLRequestHandler) 
